UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2361
1 AN ACT relating to real property.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 381.190 is amended to read as follows:
4 A[No] sale of real estate by a trustee, by virtue of a pledge or deed of trust to secure the
5 payment of debts, shall not be valid or pass the title of the property specified in the deed
6 or pledge, unless:
7 (1) The sale is pursuant[in pursuance] to a judgment of a court;[, or ]
8 (2) Is made by an assignee under a voluntary deed of assignment;[,] or[ unless ]
9 (3) The maker of the deed or pledge joins in a writing evidencing the sale.
